<h1 class="box">Universal Studios</h1>

<p class="box">I went to Universal Studios Hollywood on <strong>June 11</strong>. I went with my family and friends.</p>

</header>

<main>
<h2 class="box">Despicable Me Minion Mayhem</h2>
<p>
<center class="imagebox">
<span data-flickr-embed="true"

title="You Are About To Ride This Minion Ride"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/5739/29919120033_25405a2e02_b.jpg"
width="50%" height="50%" alt="These People Are About To Ride This Ride">
</span><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
</center>
</p>
<p class="box">
Despicable Me Minion Mayhem was <em>my favorite ride in June 2022</em>. That's because we went on that ride last before exiting.
I enjoyed going through what minions have gone through when training. I used to believe the routine body scanner but I now think the body scanner is a joke.
I was surprised in June 2019 when I realized that they no longer gave out 3D glasses. Too bad they changed the ride from 3D to 2D.
</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="https://www.universalstudioshollywood.com/web/en/us/things-to-do/rides-and-attractions/despicable-me-minion-mayhem">Despicable Me Minion Mayhem
</a>
</p>
</main>

